Comment.Text: This scenario will adapt the classifier by relearning based on its previous samples and it current ones. The labels, that are used, are the final predictions from the evidence accumulator (which comes back through the acquisition client). The spatial filter remains static. The rest of the pipeline is similar to that of p300-speller-4-online-without-monitoring. The keyboard stimulator is used to stop the scenario Otherwise it could happen that, when the stimulator sends the end-of-experiment stimulus, the classifier is not save because the scenario is already stopped. The adaptive p300 classifier box uses the relearn probabilistic lda classifier with shrinking the cov matrix to the diagonal with lambda 0.5. This is fixed in the code, should make it a parameter
